docs: The constructor
constructors.label: new

docs: Transfer approved or owned token from caller.
On success a `Transfer` event is emitted.
# Errors
Returns `TokenNotExists` error if `id` does not exist.
Returns `NotApproved` error if `from` doesn't have allowance for transferring.
Returns `SafeTransferCheckFailed` error if `to` doesn't accept transfer.
messages.label: PSP34::transfer

docs: Returns the owner of the token if any.
messages.label: PSP34::owner_of

docs: Approves `operator` to withdraw the `id` token from the caller's account.
If `id` is `None` approves or disapproves the operator for all tokens of the caller.
On success a `Approval` event is emitted.
# Errors
Returns `SelfApprove` error if it is self approve.
Returns `NotApproved` error if caller is not owner of `id`.
messages.label: PSP34::approve

docs: Returns the collection `Id` of the NFT token.
This can represents the relationship between tokens/contracts/pallets.
messages.label: PSP34::collection_id

docs: Returns the balance of the owner.
This represents the amount of unique tokens the owner has.
messages.label: PSP34::balance_of

docs: Returns `true` if the operator is approved by the owner to withdraw `id` token.
If `id` is `None`, returns `true` if the operator is approved to withdraw all owner's tokens.
messages.label: PSP34::allowance

docs: Returns current NFT total supply.
messages.label: PSP34::total_supply

docs: Mints a new token with `id`.
See [`PSP34::_mint_to`].
messages.label: PSP34Mintable::mint

docs: Returns a token `Id` owned by `owner` at a given `index` of its token list.
Use along with `balance_of` to enumerate all of ``owner``'s tokens.
The start index is zero.
messages.label: PSP34Enumerable::owners_token_by_index

docs: Returns a token `Id` at a given `index` of all the tokens stored by the contract.
Use along with `total_supply` to enumerate all tokens.
The start index is zero.
messages.label: PSP34Enumerable::token_by_index
